1
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:09,400
After a person is burned to death

2
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:11,040
their flesh turns to charcoal

3
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,280
but the bones do not

4
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:17,400
The Advisor's remains are rather suspicious

5
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:19,600
These are remains cursed dead by a paper effigy

6
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:21,000
Do you really have to take them out?

7
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,080
Why are you hiding so far away?

8
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,200
Come, come, come here

9
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,080
Don't come over

10
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:26,480
Brother Zheng Yu

11
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:34,200
The Mayor asked me to assist you

12
00:01:34,240 --> 00:01:36,200
and find a good burial place for the Advisor

13
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:40,680
The Fifth Concubine has been coming to my shop lately

14
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:42,000
She's certainly been diligent

15
00:01:43,880 --> 00:01:45,600
The Fifth Concubine comes from a family of incense and medicine

16
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:47,040
The plague has been rampant lately

17
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:49,080
I asked the Fifth Concubine to get me some medicinal powder

18
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:49,800
To isolate the bones

19
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:50,840
and prevent the spread

20
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:52,560
I really have troubled the Fifth Concubine

21
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:06,400
The Advisor died at just the right time

22
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,320
After such a fright

23
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:11,000
they will obediently hand over the money

24
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:14,040
B-But, Master

25
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:17,480
This paper effigy business is far too strange

26
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,720
Could it really be some kind of curse?

27
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:23,920
Who cares? Once we swindle the money, we run

28
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:42,240
Who is it?

29
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:55,480
Who are you trying to scare?

30
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,920
Playing ghost tricks in the dead of night

31
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:06,080
I am not afraid

32
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,720
Why is there a paper effigy here?

33
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:22,760
Who put this paper effigy here?

34
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,040
Is some family holding a funeral?

35
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:26,120
Even so, they cannot leave it here

36
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:28,320
Why is it smoking?

37
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,480
Help!

38
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:42,080
Li Zhong has returned in a paper effigy to claim lives

39
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,120
This is bad, this is bad!

40
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,720
Zheng Yu, something happened again

41
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:57,080
Water, water, water!

42
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,600
Did you find out anything?

43
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,800
Just now

44
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:07,840
Right this moment

45
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:09,760
Another one died

46
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:11,760
Three people have died in total

47
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,800
The Advisor, Zhang Baoyuan

48
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,800
And a villager, Li Tiezhu

49
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,680
And a shop owner, Chen Yuan

50
00:04:18,520 --> 00:04:21,040
Anyway, everyone in town is in a panic now

51
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:23,800
They say Li Zhong's wronged spirit clung to a paper effigy

52
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,000
and came to claim lives

53
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,560
How did Li Zhong die?

54
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,520
It is said that 12 years ago

55
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,800
Nanwan Town was just like it is now

56
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,520
a plague broke out

57
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,920
At the time, a witch doctor named Li Zhong said

58
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,960
the plague was caused by evil spirits possessing people

59
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:47,640
so he used paper effigies to drive them away

60
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:50,680
Later, young girls began vanishing one after another

61
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:54,280
Some said they saw Li Zhong with their own eyes

62
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:57,040
hide drugged girls in paper effigies and abduct them

63
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:58,880
In their fury, the townsfolk

64
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,560
burned him alive together with the paper effigy

65
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:09,000
No wonder after the paper effigy deaths began in town

66
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:13,720
everyone says Li Zhong became a paper effigy to claim lives

67
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:16,600
Anyway, every household in town fears paper effigies now

68
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:21,760
Did you remove that curse for me yet?

69
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:26,200
It takes seven times seven, 49 days

70
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,520
It is a real hassle

71
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:31,080
Anyway, I have done everything you asked lately

72
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,240
Oh, right

73
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,880
Wang Shengchang seems to be coming back in the next few days

74
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:40,440
After he returns, keep a close eye on him for me

75
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,520
Got it

76
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,480
But come to think of it, it is strange

77
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,960
Some young girls really have gone missing lately

78
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,800
Do you think it could be true?

79
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,920
Li Zhong has returned

80
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:52,920
and is targeting young girls again

81
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:55,200
You have read too many ghost stories

82
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,200
In that head of yours

83
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:57,920
stop filling it with bizarre nonsense all day

84
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,720
all right?

85
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,600
Isn't it because

86
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,920
I am with you every single day

87
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:02,760
What did you say?

88
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:05,840
N-No, no, nothing, nothing

89
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:06,960
Big brother, calm your anger

90
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,600
Look at my memory

91
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,360
I forgot the most important thing

92
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,360
The Mayor is looking for you

93
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,440
He said it is something important

94
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,640
So many talisman papers

95
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,160
Mr. Zheng

96
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:36,200
The chamber of commerce in our town

97
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:38,280
pooled enough money to invite Master Jiang

98
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:40,320
And also wishes to ask Mr. Zheng

99
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,800
to gather Li Zhong's bones and ease his wrath

100
00:06:43,080 --> 00:06:46,280
so Nanwan Town can regain peace sooner

101
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,920
As for the payment, rest assured

102
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:52,120
it will surely satisfy you

103
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:55,720
I'm doing this for the people of Nanwan Town

104
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:58,240
I won't take this money

105
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,040
Well...

106
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:00,400
Forgive my bluntness

107
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,840
Rather than give this money to a charlatan

108
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:05,120
it should treat plague patients instead

109
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,320
You mustn't say that lightly

110
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:09,040
Amitabha

111
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:11,040
That Master Jiang is very effective

112
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:17,800
You were involved in Li Zhong's burning too, right?

113
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,200
No

114
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,120
I wasn't involved

115
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:23,240
You're afraid the curse will fall on you too

116
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:26,760
No, no, no. Li Zhong harmed young girls

117
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,480
Burning him to death was what he deserved

118
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,600
He got what was coming to him

119
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,720
Who would've thought that even in death

120
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,200
he still wouldn't rest

121
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:53,760
How are you feeling?

122
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:56,000
Ever since I started these medicinal baths

123
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,360
I haven't felt as bad

124
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,680
It really works

125
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:02,240
Xu Nan, you're here

126
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:04,160
Master Xiao Shen

127
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:06,280
Since this medicinal bath is so miraculous

128
00:08:06,280 --> 00:08:09,040
then if it could be widely used in Nanwan Town

129
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:11,360
wouldn't the townsfolk recover very soon?

130
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,800
Do you know the formula for this bath?

131
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:18,120
Why is the Fifth Concubine so interested in it?

132
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:22,000
The Zhao family is also a perfumery family

133
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:23,520
I know a little medicine

134
00:08:23,960 --> 00:08:28,000
But this plague has truly baffled me

135
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,320
This is my master's exclusive secret formula

136
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:32,320
Let alone outsiders

137
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,720
he hasn't even passed it on to me

138
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,600
After all, it's his bread and butter

139
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:38,600
I see

140
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,360
I see

141
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,840
Look at me, being so careless

142
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,600
Then, brother, let's go home first

143
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:57,200
Today is the last day of the bath treatment

144
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,480
You won't need to come anymore

145
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:01,640
But I still feel very weak

146
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:05,000
I'd still like more days of treatment

147
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,440
Are you doubting my master's ability?

148
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,400
Of course not

149
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,280
The medicinal bath treatment is over

150
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,880
I understand

151
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:17,920
Then please thank Master Jiang for me

152
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:22,280
Let's go
